<?xml version="1.0"?>
<Fleet xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">
  <Name>TF Taking Forever</Name>
  <Version>3</Version>
  <TotalPoints>3000</TotalPoints>
  <FactionKey>Stock/Alliance</FactionKey>
  <Description>Difficulty: &lt;color=purple&gt;LEVY HALFCAP&lt;/color&gt;

TF Tabulated Frequencies is an escort carrier alongside five capture Sprinters. This fleet is primarily played to win on capture points on the control game mode, using your stock of bombers and their torpedoes to overmatch against enemy capture assets as well as intermediate sized anti-light assets. Aggressive and attentive use of bombers is crucial in protecting your comparably low-durability capture assets. Use of the E-44F 'Bardiche' will also allow for proactive reconnaissance, or defense of Tiny Tim from enemy flanking assets.
  </Description>
  <SortOverrideOrder xsi:nil="true" />
